# Signal Agent Workflows

## Herald Digest (highest-priority signal agent)

### What it does
Daily press release digest — scrapes, deduplicates, classifies, and emails biotech press releases.

### Done predicate (BOTH required)
- `data/press_releases/deduped/deduped_{date}.jsonl` exists
- `data/press_releases/classified/classified_{date}.jsonl` exists

If classification failed but dedupe exists: next supervisor run retries.

### Dark diagnosis

```bash
crontab -l | grep herald
ls -la ~/.hermes/logs/ | grep herald
tail -50 logs/daily_production_*.log | grep -i herald
python3 run_agent_direct.py --agent herald
python3 run_agent_direct.py --agent herald --skip-preflight
```

Root causes (in priority order):
1. hermes-mail bridge down (Herald runs but email never arrives)
2. Timeout budget exceeded (historical: 23+ min sleeps over 341 tickers)
3. Cron entry missing (WSL2 restart can lose entries)
4. Preflight gate blocking (dirty git, missing snapshot, governance hold)

### Fix: PR #266 parallelized fetcher
ThreadPoolExecutor, 12 workers, ~3-5 min (was 23+ min sequential)

## Bellringer (earnings signals)

Previews and Results are DIFFERENT cron jobs — one working + one dark = only one job failing.

```bash
crontab -l | grep -i bellringer
cat logs/bellringer_results_*.log | tail -50
python3 run_agent_direct.py --agent bellringer_results --date YYYY-MM-DD
```

## Intraday Mover Watch

- Runs during market hours (9:30 AM - 4:00 PM ET)
- Triggers on >= 5% intraday moves in watchlist tickers
- Depends on price snapshot (must run AFTER daily snapshot)
- NO_DATA error = poll before snapshot. Fix: shift first poll to after ~10:30 ET

## Catalyst Resolution Tracker (CRT)

- Agent: `crt_resolution_watcher` — ONLY agent with `mutate_data` authority
- Writes to catalyst resolution tables under orchestrator supervision
- Tracks PDUFA dates, AdCom outcomes, Ph3 readouts
- Resolution = confirmed FDA action, data release, or calendar event closure

## hermes-mail bridge (delivery infrastructure)

All signal agents depend on this for email delivery.

```bash
python3 hermes_mail_smoke_test.py
cat ~/.hermes/.env | grep SMTP
```

Fix: regenerate Gmail app password at https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
Success: smoke test email arrives in djschulz@gmail.com

