## Triage priority (when multiple agents down)

1. hermes-mail bridge — if down, nothing delivers
2. Herald Digest — highest-value daily signal
3. Bellringer — earnings preview/results
4. fleet_steward — restores health monitoring
5. Intraday Mover Watch — real-time price alerts
6. grok_biotech_watch — depends on XAI API key
7. Evening forward-shadow — watchdog, lower priority
8. postmortem memory-write — cosmetic, lowest

## Anti-patterns

- Do NOT test Herald without checking mail bridge first (silent failure)
- Do NOT mix up Bellringer previews vs results (different cron entries)
- Do NOT run intraday mover before daily snapshot exists
- Do NOT grant additional authority to signal agents (observe_only is correct)